description.plain: Kap Bambino est un duo originaire de Bordeaux, en France. C'est l'association de deux artistes : Khima France et Groupgris, de leurs vrais noms Caroline Martial et Orion Bouvier. Leur style se qualifie par un electro-rock mixé avec des sons 8-bit. Le groupe est connu pour ses prestations scéniques.

body.plain: Kap Bambino est un duo originaire de Bordeaux, en France. C'est l'association de deux artistes : Khima France et Groupgris, de leurs vrais noms Caroline Martial et Orion Bouvier. Leur style se qualifie par un electro-rock mixé avec des sons 8-bit. Le groupe est connu pour ses prestations scéniques.

songs.title: Dead Lazers
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Some terrifying and distressing images
On a blue wallpaper, in the holes of my eyes
Some cracked and rubbish stuffs
I can't sleep, I have the fucking, the fucking speed
The bass sounds go up through my pillow
And I can't stand it anymore
I'm throwing myself off the bed
I'm gonna go out, I'm gonna do it

[Chorus]
I want to see dead lazers in the night
I don't care about the distance
I want to see dead lazers in the night
It's the only thing I want

[Verse 2]
I want to see dead lazers in the night
Those we can see flirting with the stars
Before crashing on the empty highways
They bring you up to a vital point
In the middle of the greyness
On the edge of the city
Above the industrial zones
They are kings and queens
On the roof of the disco
That's where I'm going to

[Chorus]
I want to see dead lazers in the night
I don't care about the distance
I want to see dead lazers in the night
It's the only thing I want

[Verse 3]
I arrive, I draw a circle around myself
Nobody talks, everybody dances
Dancing for the sake of dancing
Letting out for the sake of letting out, for the sake of letting out
We don't care about the rest
We'll see that closely
Farther, higher, we'll be better
Soon we'll be tired
Everything will calm down in the morning
Maybe, at last, we'll be fi-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

[Outro Instrumental]
